author: CNET
description: The OnePlus 15 is getting it’s global launch this week on November 13. It’s one of the first to run the Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5, Qualcomm's next-generation chip for high-end phone, and features three 50-megapixel rear cameras, along with a selfie shooter on the front. Let’s unbox it in the color sand storm. #unboxing #oneplus15 #oneplus #mobile #android
title: Unboxing the New OnePlus 15 in Sand Storm
